{
  "video_id": "Y2byvwuD3C4",
  "title": "Why Netflix Is Using Anime To Take On Disney",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 770.0,
      "end_time": 3130.0,
      "text": "This is the Netflix's Originals category."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3130.0,
      "end_time": 5810.0,
      "text": "You're probably used to seeing a bunch of new shows"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 5810.0,
      "end_time": 7619.0,
      "text": "when you scroll through, but have you noticed"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 7620.0,
      "end_time": 9150.0,
      "text": "a lot more anime recently?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 9150.0,
      "end_time": 11600.0,
      "text": "It's not just because you watch \"Aggretsuko\""
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 11600.0,
      "end_time": 12110.0,
      "text": "on your lunch break."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 12110.0,
      "end_time": 14430.0,
      "text": "Netflix's Director of Anime Taito Okiura"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 14430.0,
      "end_time": 17780.0,
      "text": "said it planned to add 30 new anime series that year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 17780.0,
      "end_time": 19400.0,
      "text": "and the company has already announced"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 19400.0,
      "end_time": 22000.0,
      "text": "over a dozen anime series coming in 2019."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 22000.0,
      "end_time": 24150.0,
      "text": "Adding tons of content might sound like business"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 24150.0,
      "end_time": 26979.0,
      "text": "as usual for Netflix, but all of this anime"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 26980.0,
      "end_time": 29340.0,
      "text": "could actually be Netflix's secret weapon"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 29340.0,
      "end_time": 30762.0,
      "text": "in its fight against Disney."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 33300.0,
      "end_time": 36143.0,
      "text": "The Netflix versus Disney arc has already begun."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 37300.0,
      "end_time": 39420.0,
      "text": "Disney's own streaming service, Disney+,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 39420.0,
      "end_time": 40940.0,
      "text": "will launch in 2019."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 40940.0,
      "end_time": 42970.0,
      "text": "As the launch of Disney+ gets closer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 42970.0,
      "end_time": 45920.0,
      "text": "more and more Disney content has been leaving Netflix."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 45920.0,
      "end_time": 47820.0,
      "text": "There was a time when a new \"Avengers\" movie"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 47820.0,
      "end_time": 50460.0,
      "text": "was almost guaranteed to show up on Netflix,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 50460.0,
      "end_time": 52450.0,
      "text": "but that's no longer the case now"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 52450.0,
      "end_time": 54360.0,
      "text": "that their distribution deal has ended."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 54360.0,
      "end_time": 56370.0,
      "text": "Because Disney owns so much content,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 56370.0,
      "end_time": 58990.0,
      "text": "Netflix could lose big names"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 58100.0,
      "end_time": 60170.0,
      "text": "like Pixar, Lucasfilm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 60170.0,
      "end_time": 62470.0,
      "text": "Marvel, and even 20th Century Fox,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 62470.0,
      "end_time": 63900.0,
      "text": "and Disney isn't the only company"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 63900.0,
      "end_time": 65610.0,
      "text": "launching their own streaming service."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 65610.0,
      "end_time": 68330.0,
      "text": "WarnerMedia, the parent company of The CW,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 68330.0,
      "end_time": 72120.0,
      "text": "HBO, and DC, is launching a new service in 2019."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 72120.0,
      "end_time": 75590.0,
      "text": "So besides Disney's content, Netflix might also have"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 75590.0,
      "end_time": 78240.0,
      "text": "to say \"goodbye\" to films and shows owned by WarnerMedia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 78240.0,
      "end_time": 80170.0,
      "text": "like \"Friends\" and \"Riverdale.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 80170.0,
      "end_time": 82100.0,
      "text": "As more entertainment companies start their own"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 82100.0,
      "end_time": 84149.0,
      "text": "streaming services, Netflix will be forced"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 84150.0,
      "end_time": 86300.0,
      "text": "to rely on its own original content,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 86300.0,
      "end_time": 88160.0,
      "text": "But just like Midoriya cleaning up the beach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 88160.0,
      "end_time": 89353.0,
      "text": "Netflix has been busy."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 92400.0,
      "end_time": 93820.0,
      "text": "Over the past few years, Netflix has"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 93820.0,
      "end_time": 96139.0,
      "text": "ramped up production of original content,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 96140.0,
      "end_time": 97860.0,
      "text": "producing more than five times"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 97860.0,
      "end_time": 100750.0,
      "text": "the number of shows in 2018 than in 2016,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 100750.0,
      "end_time": 102680.0,
      "text": "and analysts think Netflix could spend"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 102680.0,
      "end_time": 106590.0,
      "text": "around $15 billion on original content in 2019."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 106590.0,
      "end_time": 109920.0,
      "text": "For comparison, HBO usually spends around $2 billion."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 109920.0,
      "end_time": 111810.0,
      "text": "In addition to its live action shows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 111810.0,
      "end_time": 114190.0,
      "text": "Netflix has added original anime series,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 114190.0,
      "end_time": 116940.0,
      "text": "like \"Castlevania\" and \"Devilman Crybaby,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 116940.0,
      "end_time": 118580.0,
      "text": "and they have plenty of anime classics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 118580.0,
      "end_time": 120789.0,
      "text": "like \"Fullmetal Alchemist\" and \"Bleach,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 120790.0,
      "end_time": 123330.0,
      "text": "but Netflix isn't just buying a lot of anime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 123330.0,
      "end_time": 124679.0,
      "text": "they're changing the way deals"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 124680.0,
      "end_time": 126780.0,
      "text": "are made in the anime industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 126780.0,
      "end_time": 128640.0,
      "text": "Normally, several different companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 128639.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133790.0,
      "text": "negotiate together to produce, fund, and distribute a show."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 133800.0,
      "end_time": 135990.0,
      "text": "That way, the risk is distributed across all the companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 135990.0,
      "end_time": 137790.0,
      "text": "Netflix, on the other hand, is willing"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 137790.0,
      "end_time": 140290.0,
      "text": "to take on more of the risk on its own."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 140290.0,
      "end_time": 142620.0,
      "text": "In March, Netflix announced partnerships"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 142620.0,
      "end_time": 144840.0,
      "text": "with three Japanese production houses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 144840.0,
      "end_time": 147240.0,
      "text": "adding to the two partnerships it already had."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 147240.0,
      "end_time": 148840.0,
      "text": "These production houses will create"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 148840.0,
      "end_time": 151320.0,
      "text": "five new anime series for Netflix."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 151320.0,
      "end_time": 153490.0,
      "text": "Working conditions in the anime industry"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 153500.0,
      "end_time": 156670.0,
      "text": "can be strenuous with long hours and slim margins."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 156670.0,
      "end_time": 159490.0,
      "text": "Many are hoping that direct deals with Netflix"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 159500.0,
      "end_time": 161370.0,
      "text": "could allow for greater creative freedom"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 161370.0,
      "end_time": 163340.0,
      "text": "and larger profits for production houses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 163340.0,
      "end_time": 166820.0,
      "text": "and because Netflix is available in over 190 countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 166820.0,
      "end_time": 169410.0,
      "text": "it's possible that having these anime series on Netflix"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 169410.0,
      "end_time": 171160.0,
      "text": "could bring in a broader audience."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 171160.0,
      "end_time": 172390.0,
      "text": "But why is Netflix putting"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 172390.0,
      "end_time": 175279.0,
      "text": "so much focus on anime specifically?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 175280.0,
      "end_time": 177280.0,
      "text": "Anime could be a big differentiator"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 177280.0,
      "end_time": 179660.0,
      "text": "between Netflix and Disney+."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 179660.0,
      "end_time": 182930.0,
      "text": "Disney's original content doesn't include any anime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 182930.0,
      "end_time": 184700.0,
      "text": "and Disney has said that"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 184700.0,
      "end_time": 186300.0,
      "text": "their service will be family-oriented."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 186300.0,
      "end_time": 189290.0,
      "text": "So it probably won't include mature content"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 189290.0,
      "end_time": 192340.0,
      "text": "seen in shows like Netflix's \"Devilman Crybaby.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 192340.0,
      "end_time": 195960.0,
      "text": "Having an entire category of content that Disney+ lacks"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 195960.0,
      "end_time": 198680.0,
      "text": "could be a huge advantage for Netflix,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 198680.0,
      "end_time": 200700.0,
      "text": "especially since demand for anime"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 200700.0,
      "end_time": 203700.0,
      "text": "has continued to grow over the last decade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 203700.0,
      "end_time": 205650.0,
      "text": "but not everyone is happy about Netflix announcing"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 205650.0,
      "end_time": 208240.0,
      "text": "that they're gonna combine with all of this anime."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 208240.0,
      "end_time": 209730.0,
      "text": "We're gonna combine?"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 209730.0,
      "end_time": 210100.0,
      "text": "They're gonna combine."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 210100.0,
      "end_time": 211200.0,
      "text": "They're gonna combine!"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 211200.0,
      "end_time": 212609.0,
      "text": "Funimation's President"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 212610.0,
      "end_time": 215320.0,
      "text": "Gen Fukunaga heavily criticized Netflix"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 215320.0,
      "end_time": 216450.0,
      "text": "when it acquired the rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 216450.0,
      "end_time": 219190.0,
      "text": "to stream \"Neon Genesis Evangelion.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 219190.0,
      "end_time": 222250.0,
      "text": "Fukunaga and others worry that good anime series"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 222250.0,
      "end_time": 224840.0,
      "text": "will get buried in Netflix's large library"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 224840.0,
      "end_time": 227450.0,
      "text": "instead of getting the larger release they deserve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 227450.0,
      "end_time": 229300.0,
      "text": "and Netflix isn't without competition"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 229300.0,
      "end_time": 230900.0,
      "text": "in the anime streaming space."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 230900.0,
      "end_time": 234270.0,
      "text": "Anime streaming giant Crunchyroll, now owned by AT&T,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 234270.0,
      "end_time": 237920.0,
      "text": "boasts 45 million users and 2 million subscribers."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 237920.0,
      "end_time": 240869.0,
      "text": "In March, Crunchyroll announced an expanded partnership"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 240870.0,
      "end_time": 242940.0,
      "text": "with Adult Swim, allowing Adult Swim"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 242940.0,
      "end_time": 246100.0,
      "text": "to air more of the content available on Crunchyroll on TV."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 246100.0,
      "end_time": 248600.0,
      "text": "A similar agreement allowed Adult Swim"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 248600.0,
      "end_time": 250450.0,
      "text": "to air \"Mob Psycho 100\" last year."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 250450.0,
      "end_time": 253299.0,
      "text": "Hulu also boasts an impressive anime library,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 253300.0,
      "end_time": 255840.0,
      "text": "and it has even acquired exclusive streaming rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 255840.0,
      "end_time": 257579.0,
      "text": "to \"One Punch Man\" season 2,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 257579.0,
      "end_time": 260599.0,
      "text": "and now that Disney owns a 60% stake in Hulu,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 260600.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263569.0,
      "text": "they might have an opening to the anime world after all."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 263569.0,
      "end_time": 267650.0,
      "text": "Netflix's anime journey is less of a Netero versus Meruem"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 267650.0,
      "end_time": 270659.0,
      "text": "and more of an Eren Yeager versus a world of titans."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 270660.0,
      "end_time": 272460.0,
      "text": "We'll have to wait to see the broader impacts"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 272460.0,
      "end_time": 275219.0,
      "text": "of Netflix's anime investment, but all this content"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 275220.0,
      "end_time": 277710.0,
      "text": "is definitely good news for anime fans."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 277710.0,
      "end_time": 279340.0,
      "text": "There are fewer barriers than ever"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 279340.0,
      "end_time": 282429.0,
      "text": "for fans across the globe to get into new anime series."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 282430.0,
      "end_time": 285730.0,
      "text": "There's going to be a lot to watch in 2019."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 285730.0,
      "end_time": 288643.0,
      "text": "Our My Lists won't be getting shorter anytime soon."
    }
  ]
}